
Create a framework so that the same datasets can be rendered with python scripts

The user should be able to change:-
1. Height of the cameras
2. Angle of rotation of the cameras
3. Height of the 2 hands
4. Rotation and gesture of the hands.
5. Environment maps can be added and changed.
6. Occluding objects needs to be added if user desires so/
7. The bones should be controllable.
8. Proper framwork has to be written
9. Depth maps factors should be changed.

